cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SD 

This paper deals with video decomposition and separation of layers, which is a problem in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also introduces a new neural network architecture, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.MM - Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the use of external cues such as audio, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI - Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves experimentation and evaluation of the proposed approach, which falls under the category of software development (cs.SD - Software Engineering). Finally, the paper discusses the training procedure and optimization of the proposed model, which is related to the category of machine learning (cs.LG - Machine Learning).
